ưng anh ấy ẩn chứa một bí mật có thể đảo lộn cuộc sống của mình—anh ấy không thể sử dụng phép thuật! Khi anh ta phát hiện ra, thay vì cuộc sống của anh ta kết thúc, anh ta bất ngờ đăng ký vào trường phép thuật, nơi anh ta phải đánh bại cuộc thi!</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"204832","season":1,"vote_average":8.323,"vote_count":606},"modified":"2023-06-18T15:17:03.000Z","cast":["Chiaki Kobayashi","Reiji Kawashima","Ishikawa Kaito","Takuya Eguchi","Reina Ueda","Hiroaki Hirata","Hiroshi Watanabe"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Chiaki Kobayashi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chiaki Kobayashi","tmdb_id":2279389,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/o0XZFXc50z28ICUpvfZ1QcTL2Yt.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2279389"},{"name":"Reiji Kawashima","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Reiji Kawashima","tmdb_id":2710568,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tJriYA3tctzKP3ZnAwsxkey9iyU.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2710568"},{"name":"Ishikawa Kaito","name_vi":"Ishikawa Kaito","name_original":"Kaito Ishikawa","tmdb_id":1324666,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fzjIkotjUHHs3wgftM9tqdsG8ph.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1324666"},{"name":"Takuya Eguchi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Takuya Eguchi","tmdb_id":1248374,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hPPhUp0mM65Lc87Q8WXUEmGQAXx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1248374"},{"name":"Reina Ueda","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Reina Ueda","tmdb_id":1452028,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2WV61uVU7y6XGYqNHLMpP0sApdu.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1452028"},{"name":"Hiroaki Hirata","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Hiroaki Hirata","tmdb_id":84505,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mMWEdlssJm3TVuXW4Wb7pQeX20Z.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/84505"},{"name":"Hiroshi Watanabe","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Hiroshi Watanabe","tmdb_id":2920591,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t